        {
            "title": "對沖基金Gen2在與三星證券的糾紛中尋求1.37億美元賠償",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 總部位於香港的對沖基金Gen2 Partners Ltd.尋求向三星的三家金融公司索賠逾1.37億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞看到的訴狀副本顯示，Gen2 Funds本周在香港高等法院對三星證券、Samsung Hedge Asset Management Co.和Samsung Securities (Asia) Ltd.提起索賠。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">訴訟涉及新冠疫情期間市場動盪引發的一起合同糾紛。當時，一支Gen2基金暫停了贖回，以保護投資者和基金自身利益。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-34f9e88b-576e-3732-95ff-332d924989b0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Gen2稱這些三星實體及其員工的行為給其造成了損失，因而尋求賠償和禁令救濟。該對沖基金指控它們擾亂了基金運營，對其與主經紀商的融資安排造成不利影響，迫使其清算資產，導致投資者蒙受損失並損害了其聲譽。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hedge Fund Seeks $137 Million in Dispute With Samsung Securities</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Youkyung Lee、Cat Barton、Yoolim Lee.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91gen2%E5%9C%A8%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%B3%BE%E7%B4%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%821-37%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F-062243096.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 15:06:14",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台灣利率市場：IRS與10年公債利率回落；國庫券買氣降 資金分配不均",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 川普宣布達成格陵蘭相關框架推動美債隔夜反彈，日本超長期國債亦自恐慌情緒持續回穩。台灣5年期IRS周四回落至2.1%下方，暫止本周升勢；10年期公債殖利率則自5個月高點小幅回跌。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財政部標售273天期國庫券，投標倍數1.38倍，為各天期國庫券標售自去年2月以來最低，當時亦為273天期，而倍數為1.26倍</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標售貼現率1.256%，與目前10年公債利差15.4基點</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據票券商與銀行人士稱，銀行之間資金分配不均，且部份銀行對於農曆年因素較為保守以對，利率維持在近期區間內。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據一位銀行資金調度人士稱，各家資金有些不均，因此上門找錢或丟錢的都有；與銀行間短天期拆款利率目前持平在1.15%-1.20%</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持續觀察農曆年前的季節性緊縮因素何時發酵，包括地方政府借款動撥以及企業發放獎金等等</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據兩位票券商人士表示，各家資金供應每天變化較大但整體不至於找錢無門；部份落點在農曆年假期後的短票利率可以比照年前，因為天期也接近30天</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承作近30天期、落點在農曆年假前的自保短票利率成交主要在1.44%-1.45%，持平上日</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">短票落點在年後的主要成交在約1.45%-1.47%，視天期而定；上日在約1.46%-1.47%</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承做跨月拆款在約1.40%-1.415%</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣短票市場：30天自保票上交易日平均利率1.455%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣債券發行預覽：摩根士丹利金融；花旗環球證券控股</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場動態</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博追蹤櫃買中心數據，10年熱券成交在1.41%，跌1基點；成交3億元</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5年熱券電子盤無成交</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台股加權指數上漲1.5%，報31705.42點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間下午1:34，據彭博數據，5年期利率交換報2.0975%，跌2.75基點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國10年期國債殖利率紐約尾盤報4.2428%，亞洲盤中報4.2488%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間下午12:00，據拆款中心數據，隔夜拆款加權平均利率在0.824%， 區間在0.805%-0.825%，上日收在0.819%</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上交易日當日超額準備為390億元台幣；本提存期累計超額準備為5583億元台幣，加計前期1%超額準備為9696億元台幣</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至上交易日，央行定存單未到期餘額為7兆4006.95億元台幣，上日減發173.5億元</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重點關注</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普宣布就格陵蘭達成未來協議的「框架」 不實施先前威脅的關稅</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華爾街巨擘格裡芬稱日本國債大甩賣對美國政客可謂當頭棒喝</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本出口連續第四個月成長 料給央行漸進加息提供支撐</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普暗示聯儲會主席人選或已敲定 稱鮑威爾若留任理事恐難如意</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國貿易代表格裡爾稱不確定美國能否與中國達成全面貿易協議</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-irs%E8%88%8710%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AC%E5%82%B5%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-%E5%9C%8B%E5%BA%AB%E5%88%B8%E8%B2%B7%E6%B0%A3%E9%99%8D-%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%9D%87-060611192.html",
