            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "委內瑞拉議會將討論石油行業改革 勢將打破國家壟斷局面",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"委內瑞拉議會將討論石油行業改革 勢將打破國家壟斷局面\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UmRJFJGCVZHuykoHdmI_Gg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/1961b410-f73b-11f0-9687-12073bd98c79\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">委內瑞拉議會將討論石油行業改革 勢將打破國家壟斷局面</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9-%E5%8B%A2%E5%B0%87%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B4%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%A3%9F%E6%96%B7%E5%B1%80%E9%9D%A2-015432494.html",
