        {
            "title": "韓國股市KOSPI指數創歷史新高 人工智能需求推動市場飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 韓國股市基準指數上漲，突破了總統李在明期待的5000點目標，人工智能AI驅動的需求推動了這個科技密集型市場的發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">KOSPI指數一度上漲2.2%，至5015.73點，主要受到三星電子、SK海力士和現代汽車等重量級股票的帶動。該指數在過去12個月中上漲超過90%，成為全球表現最佳的指數。韓元兌美元周四下跌0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">股市上漲凸顯了韓國從周期性出口市場向全球人工智能AI熱潮核心受益者的轉變，這得益於其在數據中心關鍵記憶晶片領域的統治地位。對於三星電子和SK海力士而言，存儲器價格上漲已轉化為盈利成長和股價上漲。指數突破5000點大關也標志著一個政治里程碑，對於李在明所承諾的解決長期以來拖累估值的治理缺陷是個助力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d54accf7-a2c0-30ef-86dc-80ca70526486-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rQ9LJETYXFn8rnWB3ffjRQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e29bb84cb3fe9b3bb5fb023fe927e7ea\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">進入1月份以來，這個基準股指只有一個交易日沒有上漲。多頭認為，這波漲勢還有延續空間，直到所謂的「韓國折扣」小時，這說的是與公司治理不善相關的長期估值不足。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">即使KOSPI處於歷史高位，但其估值在關鍵指標上仍落後於區域內其他指數。該指數的市淨率約為1.6倍，低於MSCI新興市場指數和台灣加權指數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題South Korea’s Kospi Tops 5,000 as AI Demand Fuels Market Surge</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Youkyung Lee.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82kospi%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-002322069.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 10:09:40",
